    "metadata": {
        "skybox": "sky1-blue.png",
        "sysdescription": "Serving as the political and logistical heart of the Ximni Confederation, Isscar became the de facto capital when the population of Renaera could no longer sustain open governance. The temperate world of Issen Prime hosts the Confederation Forum \u2014 an immense orbital complex where votes are transmitted in real time from across the Confederation. Isscar\u2019s orbital lanes are crowded with freighters and jump couriers, and the system\u2019s twin suns make navigation challenging, leading to frequent \u201cshadow drift\u201d incidents when ships miscalculate their approach vectors. The Isscar Jump Nexus is a key Jump Point.",
